      <details class=\"archive-ctm__item\">\n        <summary class=\"archive-ctm__summary\">\n          <span class=\"archive-ctm__title\">Bukez Finest</span>\n          <span class=\"archive-ctm__meta\">Brand Redesign / Music / Social Assets</span>\n        </summary>\n        <div class=\"archive-ctm__body\">\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__split\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__splitItem\">\n   <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Bukez---Bassweight_LOGO-EDITBALE-01.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"Bukez Finest brand redesign artwork 1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__splitItem\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Default-pic.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"Bukez Finest brand redesign artwork 2\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Default-pic_1.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"Bukez Finest brand redesign artwork 3\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Bukez---Bassweight_LOGO-EDITBALE-12.jpg_1.jpg\" alt=\"Bukez Finest brand redesign artwork 4\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Bukez---Bassweight_LOGO-EDITBALE-09.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"Bukez Finest brand redesign artwork 5\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Bukez---Bassweight_LOGO-EDITBALE-08.jpg_1.jpg\" alt=\"Bukez Finest brand redesign artwork 6\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Bukez---Bassweight_LOGO-EDITBALE-05.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"Bukez Finest brand redesign artwork 7\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Bukez---Bassweight_LOGO-EDITBALE-04.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"Bukez Finest brand redesign artwork 8\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n     <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Bukez_FB_1.jpg_1.jpg\" alt=\"Bukez Finest brand redesign artwork 9\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"333\"> \n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Bukez_Twitter.jpg_1.jpg\" alt=\"Bukez Finest brand redesign artwork 10\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"252\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Bukez_FB_2.jpg_1.jpg\" alt=\"Bukez Finest brand redesign artwork 11\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"333\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__text\">\n            Artwork and creative direction for German Dubstep and bass music producer Bukez Finezt branding redesign. Encompassing both a logo and social media collateral.\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </details>\n\n      <details class=\"archive-ctm__item\">\n        <summary class=\"archive-ctm__summary\">\n          <span class=\"archive-ctm__title\">Melbourne City Cider</span>\n          <span class=\"archive-ctm__meta\">Packaging / Label Design</span>\n        </summary>\n        <div class=\"archive-ctm__body\">\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/1_3.jpg\" alt=\"Melbourne City Cider label design artwork 1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/2.jpg\" alt=\"Melbourne City Cider label design artwork 2\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/3_1.jpg\" alt=\"Melbourne City Cider label design artwork 3\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__text\">\n            Melbourne City Cider came to me looking to design a label for the cider release. The brief was to design something that would be striking to young upper-class business people of Melbourne, with a refined colour scheme that wasn&#x27;t hard on the eye.\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </details>\n\n      <details class=\"archive-ctm__item\">\n        <summary class=\"archive-ctm__summary\">\n          <span class=\"archive-ctm__title\">Implicate Spatial Reality</span>\n          <span class=\"archive-ctm__meta\">Experimental / Motion / Editorial Feature</span>\n        </summary>\n        <div class=\"archive-ctm__body\">\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__video\">\n            <iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WEDec2h62Fs\" title=\"Implicate Spatial Reality video\"></iframe>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__text\">\n            At the end of last year Its Nice That put out an open brief to think of one word which best summed up your 2017, and then incorporate your word into any form of visual. The word that I chose was “Exhausted”. I was lucky enough to have my piece shared on their blog.\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </details>\n\n      <details class=\"archive-ctm__item\">\n        <summary class=\"archive-ctm__summary\">\n          <span class=\"archive-ctm__title\">Barcito</span>\n          <span class=\"archive-ctm__meta\">Hospitality / Menus / Art Direction</span>\n        </summary>\n        <div class=\"archive-ctm__body\">\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__split\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__splitItem\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/B-1_1.jpg\" alt=\"Barcito hospitality menu design artwork 1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__splitItem\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Bb-11.jpg\" alt=\"Barcito hospitality menu design artwork 2\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Bb-10.jpg\" alt=\"Barcito hospitality menu design artwork 3\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Bb-9.jpg\" alt=\"Barcito hospitality menu design artwork 4\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Bb-8.jpg\" alt=\"Barcito hospitality menu design artwork 5\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Bb-8_1.jpg\" alt=\"Barcito hospitality menu design artwork 6\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Bb-6.jpg\" alt=\"Barcito hospitality menu design artwork 7\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\"