\">Illustration / Apparel</span>\n        </summary>\n        <div class=\"archive-ctm__body\">\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__split\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__splitItem\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/the_quiet_life_break_on_through_t_white_back.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"The Quiet Life apparel illustration 1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__splitItem\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/the_quiet_life_otherside_relaxed_snapback_white.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"The Quiet Life apparel illustration 2\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"archive-ctm__split\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__splitItem\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/the_quiet_life_otherside_relaxed_snapback_black_grande.jpg_1.jpg\" alt=\"The Quiet Life apparel illustration 3\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__splitItem\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/the_quiet_life_break_on_through_t_white.jpg_1.jpg\" alt=\"The Quiet Life apparel illustration 4\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/SBT_7981_grande.jpg_1.jpg\" alt=\"The Quiet Life apparel illustration 5\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"870\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Screen-Shot-2017-05-10-at-7.18.54-PM_1.jpg\" alt=\"The Quiet Life apparel illustration 6\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"896\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Screen-Shot-2017-05-10-at-7.19.07-PM_1.jpg\" alt=\"The Quiet Life apparel illustration 7\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"892\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__text\">\n            Artwork and creative direction for Quiet Life.\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </details>\n\n      <details class=\"archive-ctm__item\">\n        <summary class=\"archive-ctm__summary\">\n          <span class=\"archive-ctm__title\">Hard Grime</span>\n          <span class=\"archive-ctm__meta\">Festival Branding / Custom Type / Campaign Design</span>\n        </summary>\n        <div class=\"archive-ctm__body\">\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__split\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__splitItem\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/HG_1_1.jpg\" alt=\"Hard Grime festival branding artwork 1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__splitItem\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/HG_7.jpg\" alt=\"Hard Grime festival branding artwork 2\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/HG_6_1.jpg\" alt=\"Hard Grime festival branding artwork 3\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/HG_5_1.jpg\" alt=\"Hard Grime festival branding artwork 4\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/HG_4_1.jpg\" alt=\"Hard Grime festival branding artwork 5\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/HG_3_1.jpg\" alt=\"Hard Grime festival branding artwork 6\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/HG_2.jpg\" alt=\"Hard Grime festival branding artwork 7\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/HG_1-1.jpg\" alt=\"Hard Grime festival branding artwork 8\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__text\">\nArtwork and creative direction for Hard Grime Fesival. The brief was pretty simple, which was to move away from the darker themed art that they had in previous years for something brighter, and more fun (with emphasis on the fun). The project consists of numerous digital elements with some print design and a custom typeface.\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </details>\n\n      <details class=\"archive-ctm__item\">\n        <summary class=\"archive-ctm__summary\">\n          <span class=\"archive-ctm__title\">Argyle House 5th Birthday</span>\n          <span class=\"archive-ctm__meta\">Hospitality / Event Campaign</span>\n        </summary>\n        <div class=\"archive-ctm__body\">\n         <div class=\"archive-ctm__split\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__splitItem\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/1_5.jpg\" alt=\"Argyle House 5th Birthday campaign artwork 1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"704\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__splitItem\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/22.jpg\" alt=\"Argyle House 5th Birthday campaign artwork 2\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__video\">\n            <iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/tDcojNqRcAg\" title=\"Argyle House video\"></iframe>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__text\">\nArtwork and creative direction for Argyle’s 5th Birthday Party. The Art Direction taken was themed around key birthdays like 18th’s, 21st’s.\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </details>\n\n      <details class=\"archive-ctm__item\">\n        <summary class=\"archive-ctm__summary\">\n          <span class=\"archive-ctm__title\">NYE Street Party</span>\n          <span class=\"archive-ctm__meta\">Event Branding / Type-led Campaign</span>\n        </summary>\n        <div class=\"archive-ctm__body\">\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/N-2_1.jpg\" alt=\"NYE Street Party event branding artwork 1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/N-7_1.jpg\" alt=\"NYE Street Party event branding artwork 2\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/N-6.jpg\" alt=\"NYE Street Party event branding artwork 3\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/N-5_1.jpg\" alt=\"NYE Street Party event branding artwork 4\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/N-4_1.jpg\" alt=\"NYE Street Party event branding artwork 5\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/N-3_1.jpg\" alt=\"NYE Street Party event branding artwork 6\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__video\">\n            <iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QtlmK2JJCXQ\" title=\"NYE Street Party video\"></iframe>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__text\">\n            2016 Art direction that I worked on for The Cambridge Hotel New Years Eve Street Party. The brief was to create a fun type based design, that could be correlated throughout marketing collateral.\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </details>\n\n      <details class=\"archive-ctm__item\">\n        <summary class=\"archive-ctm__summary\">\n          <span class=\"archive-ctm__title\">Northlane</span>\n          <span class=\"archive-ctm__meta\">Band Design / Art Direction Collaboration</span>\n        </summary>\n        <div class=\"archive-ctm__body\">\n         <div class=\"archive-ctm__split\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__splitItem\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/northlane_icosahedron_sweater_lg_o.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"Northlane apparel design artwork 1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"1300\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__splitItem\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/northlane_icosahedron_tank_lg_o.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"Northlane apparel design artwork 2\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"1300\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__text\">\n            Design I produced for my good friends in the band Northlane, Art Direction provided by the lead singer of the band.\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </details>\n\n      <details class=\"archive-ctm__item\">\n        <summary class=\"archive-ctm__summary\">\n          <span class=\"archive-ctm__title\">Safe Events</span>\n          <span class=\"archive-ctm__meta\">Music Event Branding / Digital + Motion</span>\n        </summary>\n        <div class=\"archive-ctm__body\">\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__split\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__splitItem\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Safe-1_1.jpg\" alt=\"Safe Events music event branding artwork 1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__splitItem\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Safe-9.jpg\" alt=\"Safe Events music event branding artwork 2\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Safe-8.jpg\" alt=\"Safe Events music event branding artwork 3\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Safe-7.jpg\" alt=\"Safe Events music event branding artwork 4\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Safe-7_1.jpg\" alt=\"Safe Events music event branding artwork 5\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Safe-6.jpg\" alt=\"Safe Events music event branding artwork 6\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Safe-6_1.jpg\" alt=\"Safe Events music event branding artwork 7\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Safe-5.jpg\" alt=\"Safe Events music event branding artwork 8\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Safe-4.jpg\" alt=\"Safe Events music event branding artwork 9\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Safe-3.jpg\" alt=\"Safe Events music event branding artwork 10\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Safe-3_1.jpg\" alt=\"Safe Events music event branding artwork 11\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3\">\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Safe-2.jpg\" alt=\"Safe Events music event branding artwork 12\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Safe-2_1.jpg\" alt=\"Safe Events music event branding artwork 13\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"archive-ctm__gallery3Item\">\n    <img class=\"zoomable\" src=\"/images/Safe-1.jpg\" alt=\"Safe Events music event branding artwork 14\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__video\">\n            <iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OFjGMgvnqFY\" title=\"Safe Events video\"></iframe>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"archive-ctm__text\">\n            Artwork and creative direction for Safe, Safe is a brand that brings the sound of the UK to the suburbs of Brisbane, the brief was to create a design that reflected that raw nature of the music that the brand loves.\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </details>\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>";
